From upstream PR: https://github.com/zaphoyd/websocketpp/pull/1164

This patch backports Asio 1.30+ and Boost 1.87 compatibility fixes 
that are currently unmerged in the official zaphoyd repository. 
It replaces deprecated boost::asio::io_context::strand::wrap 
with boost::asio::bind_executor to avoid deprecation crashes.

